15 WHEREAS, towns, cities, and counties, through their local and state arts agencies and
16 councils representing thousands of arts and cultural organizations, celebrate the value and
17 importance of arts and culture in the lives of Georgians and the health of thriving
18 communities during Georgia Arts Day.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
20 the members of this body recognize February 2, 2025, as Georgia Arts Day in Georgia and
21 encourage communities throughout the state to celebrate and promote the arts and culture.
22 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
23 and directed to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the
24 public and the press.
